Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After landing on Punk Hazard; an island with two parts, one burning, the other frozen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats learned about the hideous experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,performed by Caesar Clown, the Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and headed off to investigate but as things got going,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy was unexpectedly approached by Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna form an alliance with the Heart Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're gonna do is kidnap the Master, right?
