Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:04:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe from when I fell? Looks like I hit my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, maybe I did, too. I have a huge headache!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We've wasted so much time. I wonder if the samurai is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You made us take this side trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we all wanted to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame that we couldn't find the Yeti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll never forget the shadows that we saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't it. Don't fool yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it was an enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to talk about whether it exists or not forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed a little. You're kind of mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very old, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like that indecisive attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Samurai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we could find traces of his wooden clogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My breasts are heavy when I run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you wanted to save that samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two! Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a footprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A trace of his wooden clogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it must be some centaur's footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this! Doesn't this look like the legendary Yeti's footprint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey hey, don't be ridiculous. --Hey hey, don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:06:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, is this for real?! There are mysterious footprints in the snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're huge, aren't they?! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And they look fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If we follow them, we will find...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,…one of nature's greatest mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Look! There are huge shadows behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me they're the Yeti...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this gas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a zudden, I can't zpeak clearly az if I kot drunk. I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Iz it an enemy attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,These KYP gas canisters
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,make you drunk and drowsy regardless of whether or not you're a heavy drinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Down below the cliff is Sector F-16 filled with terrible Ice Spikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Three, for a starter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Spikes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We left their bodies at the bottom of the cliff in Sector F-16.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you recover them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We arrived at Sector F-16.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We found three of the Straw Hats as informed. We'll recover their dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a girl - she can't fight us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if there're hundreds of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You underlings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san's body is delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I should avoid getting even a single bruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for having one, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, hunting for nature's mysteries is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Should the samurai be around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so. He's probably still looking for his torso around the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We almost made it to the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get your ass kicked already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out! Are you alright?! Samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai-san! We're calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he found his torso already and went looking for his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! He's frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone kick your ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was mysteriously paralyzed and thought I was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You just got caught in a snowstorm and froze solid, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't feel cold at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Warriors don't feel cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get yourself some clothes! You have an ability to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,T-To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because of that magic, I have a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I became not capable of swimming...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't swim, right?! We know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:12:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What I'm trying to say is my torso is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...p-probably soaking in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The water?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels like the upper half of my body is in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why you couldn't even move and you were frozen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If your body's in the water, you can't use the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of water, Brook, his torso may have fallen into the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe. I heard that lake is actually filled with seawater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still alive here so I don't think it has become food for sharks yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't know what's in that lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We better pull it out as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have to ask you to... um, go under the water for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We know! You can't swim, right? What a crappy samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you people were pirates! And I'm a total stranger to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you helping me so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm responsible for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you get your whole body back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to fight me! I'll kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh great! Now you're able to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe getting frozen makes people nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...Brownbeard-san's subordino-centaurs that we robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:14:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--Stay with me! Keep running! --Get away from the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster appeared on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to tell the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where has it been hiding on the island until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep running! It's gonna come after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, a monster? You guys are monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the pirates who robbed us earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! That's my coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about them! Just run! To the {research }institute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They got our Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook. They were coming from the lake that we saw earlier, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Yes! You got it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed, Zoro-san! And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if in fact that is the lake,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there was a mountain there before, was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiley is the embodiment of a chemical weapon explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...that occurred on Punk Hazard, four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I invented the H₂S poison gas bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked so well
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and killed everything on the island in a matter of seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:11.31,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}One year later
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.81,0:17:11.31,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}One year later
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they believe I purified the gas all over the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! No one would do such a wasteful thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I compressed it and turned it into a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This island was once covered with dead soil where no one could live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,People tend to forget tragedies in no time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but that one has lingered here all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:03.33,Sign,,0,0,363,,{\blur0.3\fad(500,630)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(455,500,\1a&H00&)\t(4870,4915,\1a&HFF&)}Former Vegapunk Lab\NThird Research Institute
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.83,0:18:03.33,Sign,,0,0,363,,{\blur0.3\fad(500,630)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}Former Vegapunk Lab\NThird Research Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:12.98,Sign,,0,0,363,,{\blur0.3\fad(660,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(615,660,\1a&H00&)}Former Vegapunk Labs\NRuins of the First and Second Research Institutes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.90,0:18:12.98,Sign,,0,0,363,,{\blur0.3\fad(660,0)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}Former Vegapunk Labs\NRuins of the First and Second Research Institutes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never let him take these children again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he was using them as his test subjects and drugged them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive the Master guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then let's just go and kidnap the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if we're too late, we can't work with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna be late. I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We got their ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Let's finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Smoker-san, how can I turn back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in my way! Stay still, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the door open yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Our enemy is inside the {research }institute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just stay out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! The door is as steady as a rock, Smo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in my body, I could easily force myself into the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power is very useful! Was it teleportation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and stay inside the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We've almost reached the {research }institute's backdoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar will probably be\Nin the main room with that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to draw them out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to find out about the drug while we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you can reach the Master that easily
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're so strong, why don't you capture the Master yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can take time to find out about the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of a problem I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that and that's why I need help from you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I just want you guys to kidnap Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.99,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,--Something's flying toward us! --It's a big bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cien Fleurs:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wham!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! He said "Wham"?! Is it a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a nice shortcut!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We will kick your ass and kidnap you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, that was supposed to be a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool! Who said anything about confronting everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.08,0:22:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.71,0:23:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A battle unfolds between Smoker's G-5 Navy men and Luffy's crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,After the violent clash, just when it seems\Nlike the {research }institute will be breached...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...Caesar's deadly weapon, Smiley, rains down upon person after person...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...throwing everyone into fear and chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"On the Verge of Annihilation\NA Deadly Monster Descends"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.35,0:23:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
